{"tid":2035130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港都應該要有千人計劃","createTime":"2020-05-25T16:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T03:49:10.000Z","uid":20473,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"593da881f4e7db8548c50c74271e26b40d98f70e","tid":2035130,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"香港而家咩環境有眼見<br />\n港獨將會由小眾變成主流<br />\n之前都有人講要另覓新香港 無論建國定建新香港 都需要極多不同領域人才<br />\n而近廿年支共有心唔俾香港自立, 大部分人才都係走去金融, 醫生,律師,建築師<br />\n幾乎冇軍事軍工, 農業, 水利, 工業人才 (或有,請指正)<br />\n所以, 有冇可能搵到同路又有興趣天份既手足去讀呢啲科目?<br />\n就算最壞情況 香港冇左,呢啲知識都夠手足安身立命"},{"pid":"163bb8523c32f940fa102b5556d7fdcb65350b80","tid":2035130,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:42:13.000Z","msg":"如果要錢, 甚至香港人夾錢供手足讀學位.<br />\n準備去打一場跨幾代人既仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a7dddf4f5bdfec082d28903fe983d015f2d1a4","tid":2035130,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"供咩學位，仲讀乜書。<br />\n係都供樓供鋪同起大廈，香港人做地主，有錢有權先有得say<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7dbdcfd70691b9cd5ae31e6a67708f9214ba96","tid":2035130,"uid":293619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"攪基金<br />\n宣誓資助"},{"pid":"09105e68da71b77a733771c05aa630708a230659","tid":2035130,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59536ca718ef7e2b54c7f7a66b8ad2f9f50881e4","tid":2035130,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"港獨之父689大力支持開城大農業🤫"},{"pid":"3366c813b5999c54055697c2db694c6ad279a299","tid":2035130,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f645f8741a26c360b292132d9b2f239c3bd91d66","tid":2035130,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dis